rows.label: qev085305_MSG0001
rows.name: Heya, Pops! Looking good. You get all that flemtide all right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0002
rows.name: ...Pops?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0003
rows.name: Boy, who the heck you think you're talkin' to? Course I did![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0004
rows.name: Thanks for bringing the old man back safely, you guys.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0004_2
rows.name: How 'bout a drink, Pops?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0005
rows.name: You're on.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0006
rows.name: Wait, so... What?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0007
rows.name:
Cole Family Rule Number One:
Every job ends with a cold one.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0008
rows.name: Not the drink for crying out loud! You just called him "Pops"![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0009
rows.name: Um...yeah. Something wrong with that?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0010
rows.name: Yes! I mean, no! I mean... Isn't he your son?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0011
rows.name: Heh... So Vandham didn't tell you? Oh that's rich.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0012
rows.name: Now I get it. "A bit of an odd couple," indeed.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0013
rows.name: The old bear was messing with us.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0014
rows.name:
Okay, now Tatsu COMPLETELY lost.
Who want to explain to Tatsu?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0015
rows.name:
So how old are you, Leland?
Somewhere in your eighties or so?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0016
rows.name: Hey now! I'm 78 years young, missy.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0017
rows.name: WHAT?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0018
rows.name: He means inside.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0019
rows.name:
My old man refused to board the White Whale
unless he got a younger mim body.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0020
rows.name:
Hey now! I just wanted a body that
matched my mental age is all.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0021
rows.name: Now how about that drink?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0022
rows.name: You got it, pops.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0023
rows.name: He's 80...and kind of hot. That is so gross.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_JNK0010
rows.name: Boast

rows.label: qev085305_SEL0011
rows.name: Claim you knew Leland was the son all along.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_JNK0020
rows.name: Confirm

rows.label: qev085305_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask if Kiefer is Leland's...son?

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0024
rows.name: Er, Leland is actually the father. Kiefer is the son.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0025_m
rows.name: Meh! And friend sounded so confident![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0025_f
rows.name: Meh! And friend sounded so confident![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0026
rows.name: That's right. ...Also, weird.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0027
rows.name:
Actually, this shoots right past weird
and goes straight to creepy.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0028
rows.name:
They are definitely an odd pair. I mean,
even separate from the whole age thing.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0029
rows.name: You said it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0030
rows.name: Leland was ditched by his son and didn't even blink.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0031
rows.name: Actually, he acted like it was expected![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0032
rows.name: And he stayed to finish the task in front of him.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0033
rows.name: Sounds like a true BLADE to me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0034
rows.name: Mission or not, abandoning your own kin like that?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0035
rows.name: Hard to see that as a positive thing.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085305_MSG0036
rows.name:
Whatever works for them, I guess. But family
means something different to me.[ST:wait ]
